@startuml
title MazarbuLib - Module / Repository Architecture

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
left to right direction

package "Repository: reboot-required/MazarbuLib" {

  package "include/" {
    [mazarbulib.h] as H
    [mazarbulib_config.h] as CFG
  }

  package "src/" {
    [mazarbulib.c] as C
  }

  package "examples/" {
    [posix.c] as EX_POSIX
    [stm32_hal.c] as EX_STM32
    [arduino.cpp] as EX_ARD
  }

  package "tests/" {
    [test_mazarbulib.c] as TEST
  }

  package "build system" {
    [CMakeLists.txt] as CMAKE
    [Makefile] as MK
    [cmake/MazarbuLibConfig.cmake.in] as CMAKECFG
    [library.json] as PIO
  }
}

CFG --> H : configuration macros
H --> C : public declarations used by implementation

EX_POSIX --> H : uses API
EX_STM32 --> H : uses API
EX_ARD --> H : uses API

TEST --> H : tests public API
TEST --> C : validates behavior indirectly

CMAKE --> C : builds static library
CMAKE --> H : exports include path
CMAKE --> TEST : optional test target
CMAKE --> EX_POSIX : optional example target

MK --> C : builds library
MK --> TEST : builds/runs tests
MK --> EX_POSIX : builds demo

PIO --> H : package metadata
PIO --> C : package metadata

note bottom of C
Core responsibilities:
- context initialization
- screen registration
- row registration
- navigation
- value formatting
- table rendering
- UART output
end note

@enduml
